Subject: Philadelphia Seminars Are Soon

Only 4 weeks left before PGS Energy Training's
downtown Philadelphia seminars. (March 5 thru 8) 

For information on upcoming PGS seminars in Philadelphia
and in downtown Houston (February and April),
call 412-279-9298 
or visit  http://www.pgsenergy.com/schedule.html

Available seminars include:
